data.description: Soft close cabinets, granite countertops, new flooring, new paint, new bathrooms, new appliances and newer fence.  Ceiling fans throughout. HVAC less than two years old. Stove and water softener less than 1 year old.  New garbage disposal. New dishwasher being installed. Large yard ready to become your own oasis.  ENCLOSED Florida room with it's own brand new HVAC adds a ton of square footage.  Dont forget the community 2 pools, playgrounds, basketball courts, soccer fields, a library and more. Too many amenities to mention with very reasonable HOA fees. Great Northside schools. Quick access to 1604 and 410. Tons of shopping and dining options near by. Hard to find a gem like this for this price point anymore.  Move in ready. The updates and upgrades are already done!!! Vacant and ready to show even on short notice.
